From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sami Saari <polartape@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 18:08:14 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] 9087: Add Fairchild F8 processor module

New processor module for the Fairchild F8 / Mostek MK3870
microprocessor family (1975). All 76 instructions implemented.

Verified against F3850 CPU Datasheet, F8 Guide to Programming,
and F8 User's Guide. Tested with real MK3870 firmware.
